('Clínica Blasi', 'Dental', 'English-speaking dental clinic in Barcelona''s Sarrià-Sant Gervasi neighborhood. Established in 1991 by Dr. José Ignacio Blasi with the goal of offering professional and personalized dental treatment based on trust. Over three decades of excellence in dental care has earned the trust and respect of the community through commitment to quality, innovation and personalized treatment. Offers comprehensive dental services including dental implants, oral surgery, orthodontics (braces and aligners), dental prostheses (crowns, bridges, dentures), periodontics (gum disease treatment), and endodontics (root canals). All treatments are adapted to each client''s individual needs. The clinic features cutting-edge technology and the team receives continuous external training to stay current with the latest dental techniques. Conveniently located on Carrer de Muntaner in the upscale Sarrià-Sant Gervasi district. English-speaking staff welcome international and expat patients.', 'C/ de Muntaner, 341, 08021 Barcelona', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', '+34 934 146 404', 'info@clinicablasi.com', 'https://clinicablasi.com/en/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
